<p class="entry-meta"><time class="entry-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2018-12-18T00:00:18+00:00">December 18, 2018</time> <span class="entry-by">by</span> <span class="entry-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/author/lace/" class="entry-author-link" itemprop="url" rel="author"><span class="entry-author-name" itemprop="name">Lace</span></a></span> </p></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><figure id="attachment_4687" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4687" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1-300x218.jpg" alt="How To Connect iPad To TV with HDMI (A Complete Guide) | Joy of Apple" width="700" height="508" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1-300x218.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1.jpg 730w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4687" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1-300x218.jpg" alt="How To Connect iPad To TV with HDMI (A Complete Guide) | Joy of Apple" width="700" height="508" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1-300x218.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ipad-pro-97-connect-to-tv-1.jpg 730w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">How To Connect iPad To TV with HDMI (A Complete Guide)</figcaption></figure>
<p>Watching a good movie on a bigger screen is ideal. Especially when the movie is so good that you don&#8217;t want to miss anything.</p><div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="1994154162"></ins>
